description:
@PrasannaDhana

The rpm figure I quoted is from this review. Yes, it is high.
The Punch isn't exactly a wind cutter too. I imagine coefficient drag is on the higher side.

@longhorn, HBX is wider than the Altroz.

HBX - 1822mm
Altroz - 1755mm

I get reminded of my daughter's KG assignment - form a sentence using 3 words in the list;

Punching the stonhenge (spelt as per the list) is an adventure.

But Tata is punching so many bags at once with this product as experiment. Good to see the positive side - Tata is trying something different!
